{"id": "1393125021605433434", "channel_id": "1393125021605433434", "type": 0, "author_id": "1203160985393696793", "author_name": "urther.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Today I played a small event of MY TURN : INFINITE MAGIC DUEL in Morimens and got immediately very nostalgic.\n\nI loved My Turn, and played it for a long time. But I had to take a break for sometime due to some other obligations. When I returned I was shocked to find out that the servers have shut down permanently.\n\nPlease I beg u it was a gem which I want to enjoy again. Heard u people were the developers of it, is it possible to relaunch it again??\n\nThank you so much for creating such wonderful masterpiece.\nLove u guys!", "timestamp": "2025-07-11T07:01:28.162000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1393125021605433434", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Please relaunch MY TURN: INFINITE MAGIC DUEL", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
